---
title: Falafel Ciabattas with Herby Garlic Fries
description: There's a new sandwich in town! These falafel ciabattas are packed with our tasty falafel, harissa-spiced hummus and mango chutney to create a flavour sensation! Throw in some herby garlic fries and harissa ketchup on the side for good measure and this dish will be sure to delight!
